BEGIN_TEXT
$PAR
On the basis of the above picture, what can we say about the following limits?
Your answer should be one of the following: a number, INF for \(\infty\), MINF
for \(-\infty\), or IND for indeterminate (ie. the picture does not provide enough
information to evaluate the limit).
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{-}}f(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{+}}f(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{-}}f'(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{+}}f'(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{-}}f''(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{+}}f''(x)=\) \{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{-}}f(x)f'(x)=\)\{ans_rule(25)\}
$BR
\(\lim_{x\to $a^{+}}(f(x)+f'(x))=\)\{ans_rule(25)\}
END_TEXT

